{"comments":"LinearRGB — Linear-light RGB molecule for color math.\n\n**WHY LINEAR RGB MATTERS:**\nsRGB applies a nonlinear \"gamma\" encoding to compress highlight detail.\nThis encoding is perceptually motivated but mathematically problematic:\n- Blending in sRGB produces incorrect results\n- Light calculations require linear values\n- Color transformations need linear input\n\n**The sRGB Transfer Function:**\nLinear → sRGB (gamma encoding):\n  if linear ≤ 0.0031308:\n    srgb = 12.92 × linear\n  else:\n    srgb = 1.055 × linear^(1/2.4) - 0.055\n\nsRGB → Linear (gamma decoding):\n  if srgb ≤ 0.04045:\n    linear = srgb / 12.92\n  else:\n    linear = ((srgb + 0.055) / 1.055)^2.4\n\n**When to use LinearRGB:**\n- Blending/compositing operations\n- Lighting calculations\n- Color space conversions (through XYZ)\n- Any additive color math\n\n**When to use sRGB:**\n- Display output\n- Storage (8-bit images)\n- CSS/web colors\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LinearRGB"],"LinearChannel"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[137,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/LinearRGB.purs","start":[137,1]},"title":"eqLinearChannel"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LinearRGB"],"LinearChannel"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[138,54],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/LinearRGB.purs","start":[138,1]},"title":"ordLinearChannel"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LinearRGB"],"LinearChannel"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[141,34],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/LinearRGB.purs","start":[140,1]},"title":"showLinearChannel"}],"comments":"Linear-light channel value (0.0-1.0, can exceed for HDR)\n\nRepresents physical light intensity before gamma encoding.\nValues are clamped to >= 0.0 (negative light is impossible).\nValues > 1.0 are allowed for HDR content.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[135,45],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/LinearRGB.purs","start":[135,1]},"title":"LinearChannel"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LinearRGB"],"LinearRGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[188,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/LinearRGB.purs","start":[188,1]},"title":"eqLinearRGB"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LinearRGB"],"LinearRGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[189,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/LinearRGB.purs","start":[189,1]},"title":"ordLinearRGB"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LinearRGB"],"LinearRGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[19